# Timber Trainer Project Landing Page

This repository contains the website for Timber Trainer - a virtual reality training system that teaches users to operate forestry machinery. The harvester simulator is designed and optimized for the Meta Quest VR headset and offers a realistic and immersive experience where users can practice controlling, navigating, and tree processing with the harvester.

### Website Hosting

The Timber Trainer page is currently hosted here - https://profile1code.github.io/timber-trainer-project-page/
It will eventually be relocated to a more permanent home.

